lyTime":"2019-11-30T19:24:58.000Z","msg":"頭超痛 因為我瞓撚咗24個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />以上<br />\n好似係由11點幾瞓撚到1點<br />\n25-26個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好問點做到 因為我唔係正常人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我好耐冇思考過人生<br />\n因為失去咗覺得痛苦自責嘅內疚功能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n基本上唔會覺得有嘢係值得唔開心<br />\n所以先唔會思考<br />\n除咗睇新聞有陣時會喊 已經好耐冇因為自己嘢而唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為真係冇嘢值得唔開心 覺得所有嘢都好小事<br />\n<br />\n覺得啲好煩嘅嘢好撚煩 係因為唔覺得係正常會有嘅一部分<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以覺得好撚煩 本身就唔需要<br />\n<br />\n本身係直情allergic<br />\n<br />\n已經過咗嗰段時期 做埋啲咁嘅嘢只有唔相稱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n頭真係好柒暈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔會點羨慕人 因為本身有嘅嘢已經唔同 點解要羨慕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對自己冇話唔滿意到會唔開心嘅地步<br />\n總之....真係好耐冇需要打一堆嘢嚟思考清自己想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但而家打緊係因為太耐冇打想打下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />...<br />\n驚要安慰人嗰陣連同理心都冇埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aa215fa119a5968baf6fa2fe49f5c29578b508b","tid":1764004,"uid":124256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"258fc520fb35e13ff9d7c90ed855b72d68ec916d","tid":1764004,"uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01b733def407187b14c2971d317e84081dc84b33","tid":1764004,"uid":124256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T18:57:29.000Z","msg":"到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T18:57:59.000Z","msg":"好心痛"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T19:28:56.000Z","msg":"又到你失戀？"},{"pid":"998137f5b1443b259c976e322955b246627db18a","tid":1764004,"uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5aa215fa119a5968baf6fa2fe49f5c29578b508b","tid":1764004,"uid":124256,"li